OL,3,CFuel prices up 10p per litre since
OL,4,Cstart of year
OL,6,FAverage petrol and diesel prices have
OL,7,Frisen by 10p per litre so far this
OL,8,Fyear, new figures show.
OL,10,FThe RAC said the average price of a
OL,11,Flitre of petrol increased by 3p to
OL,12,F150.0p in April alone.
OL,14,FIt claimed drivers are being
OL,15,F"seriously overcharged for diesel",
OL,16,Fwith average prices rising by 2p per
OL,17,Flitre to 157.8p in April.
