OL,6,FRising pump prices since the start of
OL,7,Fthe year have added around #5.50 to
OL,8,Fthe cost of filling a typical 55-litre
OL,9,Ffamily car.
OL,11,FThe RAC is calling on the Competition
OL,12,Fand Markets Authority (CMA) ` an
OL,13,Findependent non-ministerial Government
OL,14,Fdepartment ` to address "glaring
OL,15,Fissues" with fuel retailing.
