OL,6,FIt wants the regulator ` which is
OL,7,Fresponsible for monitoring prices and
OL,8,Fwill oversee the incoming PumpWatch
OL,9,Fprice transparency scheme ` to tackle
OL,10,F"unfair retailer margins which lead to
OL,11,Fdrivers getting a raw deal".
OL,13,FThe RAC said if the biggest fuel
OL,14,Fretailers charged "fairer margins" it
OL,15,Fwould benefit drivers in several ways,
OL,16,Fsuch as:
OL,18,F` Ending the "postcode lottery" which
OL,19,Fmeans some companies charge "wildly
OL,20,Fdifferent prices" across locations.
