OL,3,CFuel prices up 10p per litre since
OL,4,Cstart of year
OL,6,F` Stop so-called rocket and feather
OL,7,Fpricing, where pump prices surge when
OL,8,Fwholesale costs rise, but fall slowly
OL,9,Fwhen wholesale costs decline.
OL,11,F` Reduce fuel prices in Britain to
OL,12,Flevels in Northern Ireland, where they
OL,13,Fare consistently 5p per litre cheaper.
OL,15,FDespite the CMA expressing concern
OL,16,Fabout retailer margins earlier this
OL,17,Fyear, the average margins for a litre
OL,18,Fof petrol and diesel is 9.5p and 17.5p
OL,19,Frespectively, according to the RAC.
