OL,6,FThe long-term average margin for both
OL,7,Ffuels is around 8.0p.
OL,9,FRAC fuel spokesman Simon Williams
OL,10,Fsaid: "Drivers are once again having
OL,11,Fto dig deep just to go about their
OL,12,Fdaily lives.
OL,14,F"Our data shows petrol and diesel have
OL,15,Fnow gone up 10p a litre so far this
OL,16,Fyear on the back of further increases
OL,17,Fin April of 3p and 2p respectively.
