OL,3,CFuel prices up 10p per litre since
OL,4,Cstart of year
OL,6,F"Some of this is down to the oil price
OL,7,Fand the pound-to-dollar exchange rate
OL,8,Fmaking wholesale petrol more expensive
OL,9,Ffor retailers to buy.
OL,11,F"But unfortunately, it's also very
OL,12,Fapparent that retailers are making
OL,13,Fmassive margins on diesel.
OL,15,F"Worryingly, the CMA's warning shot
OL,16,Fabout higher retailer margins at the
OL,17,Fend of March appears to have fallen on
OL,18,Fdeaf ears, meaning drivers are once
OL,19,Fagain being seriously overcharged for
OL,20,Fdiesel."
